Controlled: same reconstruction + iters=800 restarts=3; only the sense model/loss differ.
- mixture-NLL : angle=0.179+/-0.155 turn=0.115 dist=0.216
- margin-hinge: angle=0.498+/-0.324 turn=0.369 dist=0.137
